message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your endeavors. Given its exceptional quality and value, I'm offering it to you at an exclusive price of $13500. This is a special opportunity tailored specifically for you, considering the immense worth this product holds for you personally, estimated at $12000. I trust that you'll find this offer compelling and look forward to discussing how we can finalize the transaction.
